title: Frank Borzage Collection DVD 1
description:
Seven early movies from the great American director, Frank Borzage.

All the films are in AVI format (Xvid + Lame MP3) and of very good quality considering the time period.

(1927) Seventh Heaven

(1928) Street Angel

(1929) Lucky Star

(1929) The River

(1931) Bad Girl

(1932) A Farewell to Arms (Uncut version)

(1933) Man's Castle

Also included are some webpages and photographs about Mr.Borzage
